Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}教師樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼新曲是敘事曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用作誘導的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 誘導是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍捲風的時候你沒聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要在學校裡面組建搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲取一般學生的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們雖然不會直接傷害他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾利用一下 如果妨礙作戰的話就必須排除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 就是需要她們吸引大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是NPC卻很愛追星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 她們的樂隊有著那樣的實力和魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 這樣不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敘事曲確實有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這麼安靜聆聽的話 我們不就要搞得很低調了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 那麼就不採用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼重新打起精神 現在向全員通告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音無 拉下窗簾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的任務是入侵天使領域的再挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執行時間是三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 上次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次由他來參與作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從椅子背後？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉貝 這是哪門子玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種體弱多病的有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛… 別這樣說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙沒朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3.1415926535...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是圓周率嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快停下 那個人是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我們的弱點就是全是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做隊長的別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次的入侵作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於我們的智商有限而失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這次有夢想成為天才駭客而死的他在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網名 竹山  加入作戰小組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對天使領域進行詳盡的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的是真名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 帥氣的網名被浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是由莉貝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那天使領域是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使住的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使住的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是住在什麼樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那種地方需要駭客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個地方是由電腦控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 機械城堡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡一定有什麼辦法接觸到神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是個很厲害的作戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使也會比以前更加戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Girl DeMo也像之前一樣 辦得熱鬧一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Get chance and luck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第二聯絡橋下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼覺得我是不是和他們混的太熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不過他們比起那時候的第一印象來說不像壞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}教學樓B棟 佈告欄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是之前所說的那個華麗的誘導嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 嚇到妳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你認識我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著一個大斧的前輩告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「他可是災厄的化身 要小心點!」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這個 佔領體育館真的沒有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是很危險 前所未聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這也不是臨時性的Live
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是有先行預告的Live
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師們也不會放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道會遇到什麼樣的阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 聽說這次作戰必須要用盡一切的手段吸引觀眾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Girls Dead Monster 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是唯 雖然還是誘導班打雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這樣就滿足了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是 Girls DeMo 的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？ Girls Dead Monster 很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡稱Girls DeMo！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單憑女生就有那樣的演奏功力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有不可小看的主唱兼吉他手的岩澤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還包辦了作詞跟作曲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡的歌曲是Crow Song
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副歌的轉調讓人感到出其不意而十分動聽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連歌詞也像是在描述岩澤本身一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 用來提升士氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alchemy  Alchemy可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒說完呀  Alchemy可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有美國時間陪妳去發神經
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去幫妳最喜歡的Girl DeMo工作!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就這樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}教學樓A棟 空教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 馬上重新調好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:08:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也難怪一般學生會對妳們那麼狂熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺就聽得入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說 你沒有記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的記憶...也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有聽過誰的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...由莉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是最慘的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的過去也沒有那麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那麼」?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是什麼重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法唱自己喜歡的歌 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父母常常都在吵架 家不成家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我選擇了在那些叫罵聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一旁蜷起自己的身體 視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了躲在自己的「殼」裡面就別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裡 都沒有能讓我休息的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後 我遇上了名為Sad Machine的樂團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的主唱跟我一樣 有著不幸的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他們每當精神疲弱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會用耳機塞住自己的耳朵 逃進音樂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我也嘗試了這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就像被丟在九霄雲外一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主唱代替了我去呼嘯 歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秉持著常識的人才是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣的人才是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤獨的我們才活得像人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高呼不合理 發洩忿怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破常理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我給救了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他在下雨天的垃圾場裡相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開始唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本以為什麼都沒有的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以妳的成績　要去哪裡都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 已經不想再靠父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷去唱片公司試音的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從畢業那時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就決定要離開那個屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去東京    然後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用音樂　活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...是這樣打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就彈不了吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取消今晚的廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休…息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不出話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭部受創
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦梗塞引起的失語症
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是 父母吵架的時候的誤傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我詛咒了命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡都逃不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣　我的人生在這裡結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩澤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久子　OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒記憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是　詛咒了人生無常的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也有著悲劇的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家並不是懼怕著會變成水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的所有人都想要和神抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於遭受了不公平的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就算了吧 學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 Girl DeMo的表演是我們唯一的樂趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要剝奪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是壞人一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次靠最少的人數來實行作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰時間就在今天的19：00
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,operation start
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 盡情地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 首先 入侵算是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使領域的入侵 快關上門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵電腦方面就交給竹山君了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡只不過是普通的女生房間吧 這不是犯罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是女生宿舍 快關燈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且入侵什麼電腦 不是只有一台個人電腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Password
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前沒有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 是展現我實力的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始破解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦? 看來這傢伙姑且還算有用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 這是侵犯隱私...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再吵的話我把你喉嚨整個割下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 我明明才剛對你們有所改觀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 再來一點人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alchemy？在這開頭就？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖回到宿舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要 我絕對要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你們才給我回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 請更高漲一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 能讓大家興奮的不是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使 出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 正在執行高速分析密碼的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有　請叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹山君做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有的資料都複製下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太花時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有　請叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把整個硬碟扯走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之給我們看些可疑的檔案吧　竹山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生名單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NPC…　不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是普通的名冊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡都沒有可疑的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只是犯罪行為不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘導組被壓制了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也一無所獲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要她們的音樂 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前只是縱容她們 別太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂器全部沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又不是學園祭 不會再有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 這個扔了也沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要碰那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的曲子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹山君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　請叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子　一直唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我被救贖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子救贖其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於　終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩澤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把知道的東西都整理一下吧　由莉貝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使自行開發了自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且居然跟我們製造武器的方法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊　太見外了　由莉貝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是跟我們需要用同樣的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裡引申出來　真是最壞的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡都沒有神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼天使的能力不是由神賦予的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼有必要自行開發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩澤消失到哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被天使抹除了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在演唱會途中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰將岩澤同學
